  "title": "Exploring the Origins of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga'",
  "lessonText": "In this section, we delve into the origins and significance of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' in early childhood development.",
  "data": {
    "content": "• 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' represents playful sounds made by infants.  \n• These sounds are crucial for language development.  \n• Understanding these expressions helps in recognizing emotional cues in young children.  \n• The term is often linked to early stages of communication, where infants explore sounds before forming words.  \n• As discussed in the Understanding 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' Walkthrough, these sounds play a significant role in cognitive and social development."
